        "subject": "LU-2359 fld: Make fldb reads eventually return EOF",
        "message": "LU-2359 fld: Make fldb reads eventually return EOF\n\nRework the seq_file functions backing /proc/fs/lustre/fld/srv-*/fldb\nso that reads eventually return eof. Also fix endian mismatch between\nseq_file position and fld search key.\n\nSigned-off-by: John L. Hammond <jhammond@tacc.utexas.edu>\nChange-Id: I9d9715912b54b73c5cc8a5c22df02a1eb48e4f98\n"
